GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
HOUSE BILL 517
RATIFIED BILL
AN ACT TO MAKE VARIOUS CHANGES TO THE NORTH CAROLINA NONPROFIT
CORPORATIONS ACT AND TO ALLOW A CHARITABLE ORGANIZATION'S
DISCLOSURE UNDER STATE LAW TO BE SATISFIED BY THE
ACKNOWLEDGEMENT REQUIRED FOR A TAX DEDUCTION UNDER FEDERAL
LAW AND TO MODIFY THE EMERGENCY VIDEO SUNSETS.
The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
